{"tid":1972840,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(又遲) 全新iphone 將推遲至10月才發布","createTime":"2020-04-14T19:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T04:15:11.000Z","uid":28068,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a14447ebc9759abd053a4f25f1c3d3ff688b2229","tid":1972840,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T19:09:14.000Z","msg":"智東西4月13日消息，外媒Wccftech近日報導，iPhone 12將於9月上市，但6.7英寸iPhone 12 Pro Max或將延遲至10月推出。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司現在允許員工在家中進行部分研發工作，通過視頻會議討論組件處理，由於COVID-19影響，物流運輸和零部件庫存可能不足，iPhone 12的頂配版或將延遲兩週左右推出。<br />\n<br />\n因此，5.4英寸和6.1英寸的iPhone 12可能會在9月份上市，但6.7英寸的型號要到10月才會發布。<br />\n<br />\nCOVID-19可能在一定程度上影響智能手機銷量，蘋果還可能根據情況的發展進一步推遲發佈時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">此外，即將面世的2020 iPhone SE，預計最早將於本月上市。</span></span>"},{"pid":"e0e1bc934745e059e1d98a2fda973ac87e4dbcd2","tid":1972840,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"delay夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47285614c24d6a4ce2c7f798058a419347b6292a","tid":1972840,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T19:17:53.000Z","msg":"睇完MacBook air 2020 覺得新機都會係升spec唔改樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4515561c4656d4b87f0056c3c80d713b8de29855","tid":1972840,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:41:34.000Z","msg":"delay no more"},{"pid":"6304f67ada663cc9e7274a49e46fe6314451b93d","tid":1972840,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"仲敢買支那製出口品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24d356f5f774154c48271cedcc3af3c6012b1fe","tid":1972840,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6304f67ada663cc9e7274a49e46fe6314451b93d","tid":1972840,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":